{"tid":774146,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔憤怒 發脾氣【身體語言】+兔兔腳很敏感!","createTime":"2018-08-10T05:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T05:17:28.000Z","uid":197098,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c864ff35140daa447a2ce7f45aabb8fe2b5c4043","tid":774146,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:41:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子不滿的時候會咕咕叫。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。 <br />\n<br />\n當兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對著你。(這個耳朵擺放與驚慌一樣，但坐姿不同。驚慌的兔子坐姿蹲下) 以下這隻白兔(New Zealand White Rabbit)呈現出憤怒的樣子：(兔子被撫摸或睡覺時，耳朵也是放在後面，所以要看當時情況)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/133852_ddf9c9a45551e218c4018d5c53e9f6bb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F133852_ddf9c9a45551e218c4018d5c53e9f6bb.jpeg&h=8683a9c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">垂耳兔子憤怒時耳朵會豎起，有時有一點兒向前，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放與垂耳兔驚慌時一樣，但坐姿不同。驚慌的垂耳兔坐姿蹲下) 垂耳兔子舒適時耳朵會放鬆，有時有一點兒向後。<br />\n<br />\n憤怒時如果你撫摸牠，牠可能不理會你而逃去，或撲過來咬你。就算給牠食物，牠亦可能不吃不理會你，直到一段時間後才理會你，要看傷害牠有多深。牠亦可能會不開心不聽話而隨地大便。如果主人在牠面前打開手掌(即是要求牠舔你)，對於兔子來說，這是更加不尊重牠。如果牠屁股對着你(或其他兔子)，就代表牠生悶氣。記住不要打兔子，牠永遠不會忘記的。這會令與主人關係更差，令到害怕了主人而不吃東西。<br />\n<br />\n兔子的腳是很敏感的，所以選擇籠子時，確保底部不是鐵絲綱製造，而是平的，站起來舒服的。否則，牠可能只會站在乾草上，不站在籠子內其他地方，因為鐵絲網令到牠們的腳不舒服。牠們的耳朵和脊椎也是很敏感和易受損的，所以用正確方法抱起兔子，不要抓著耳朵舉起來。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可看到兔兔憤怒而咬人，然後害怕而逃去：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4vCt0losI5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4vCt0losI5s&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=505dea98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4vCt0losI5s</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可看到主人搔垂耳兔兔的腳，兔兔憤怒而咬他:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-7q48ITxeT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-7q48ITxeT8&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=9415b812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-7q48ITxeT8</a> <br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>當兔子用下巴磨擦東西或主人(chinning)時，下巴的腺體能分泌出一種人類聞不到的氣味，以表示這是屬於牠的東西(霸地盤)。</ins>以下video 可看到兔子A 下巴磨擦兔子B的地盤，可以見到兔子B已經憤怒去嚇A，然後屁股對着A(生悶氣):</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XCansGFudNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXCansGFudNs&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=da2ef9ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XCansGFudNs</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可在3:00看到垂耳兔憤怒撲過來的時候, 就算主人給牠食物也不吃不理會他：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5mtIM4C-cXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5mtIM4C-cXc&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=25e7c242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5mtIM4C-cXc</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">怎樣令兩隻兔子和睦相處？這個video 有教，步驟簡單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmaH-d1LOxc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHmaH-d1LOxc&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e662fd87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmaH-d1LOxc</a><br />\n<br />\n更多關於兔子憤怒的身體語言: <a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/why-you-fiend/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Fwhy-you-fiend%2F&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=cb432e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/why-you-fiend/</a> <br />\n<strong><em>領養兔仔：</em></strong><a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e879df2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"234080b78722d6fb1be54e0792ede6c46034b1e1","tid":774146,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:44:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e879df2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n兔兔發夢同主人玩：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds-7b9X5x_Ro&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=df489129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro</a>"},{"pid":"1bdddac9f525876c91f4f40827a9d49bbf11029f","tid":774146,"uid":129054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61655a2fb5224e6918370e710aeccb012c7119bd","tid":774146,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"🐰領養了兔兔，改變了牠的生命！牠還會經常binky(跳兔子舞) ! 🤩<br />\n<br />\n(兔子binky是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e6471f68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a><br />\n<br />\n實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e879df2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"1fb39a11549909f0da3b1c6b64b2f90cf7818c46","tid":774146,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2